name: Azca
description:
Having recently emerged from a long period of isolation, the residents of the ancient Dwarven realm bear little resemblance to the bloodthirsty, seafaring conquerors of centuries past.

Their smithcraft is now employed throughout the world and Azca itself now hosts a burgeoning population of foreigners in its capital, which has become something of a destination for pleasure-seekers.

Over all this presides the Dragonborn monarch Amtur Ironbreaker, whose sudden amiability toward other nations seems to some to hide an inner shrewdness…
